{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a0eeb23427","title":"中共中央、国务院、中央军委重申北京卫戍部队和民兵武装指挥权的规定","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"6e7b844d86","index":0,"year":1966,"month":6,"day":19,"articleId":"a0eeb23427","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"文章","id":"c9f57d6426","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"b7a1c99161","name":"国务院"},{"id":"ddddc27d93","name":"中央军委"},{"id":"f10c9d6647","name":"中共中央"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"851a80974a","type":"title","text":"中共中央、国务院、中央军委重申北京卫戍部队和民兵武装指挥权的规定","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a0eeb23427","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"44e3cedbcb","type":"paragraph","text":"近来，发现首都地区有些单位或个人，在文化大革命运动过程中，擅自指挥调动卫戍部队和民兵武装。这种做法，极易造成混乱，有碍首都治安。","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a0eeb23427","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"86e8f1a8a7","type":"paragraph","text":"为了确保首都安全和首都地区文化大革命运动的发展，特重申，北京卫戍部队和民兵武装的指挥权，必须集中于首都工作组。卫戍部队和民兵武装的任务部署和指挥使用，都必须经首都工作组根据中央的指示作出决定，由北京卫戍区具体组织实施。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a0eeb23427","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"41d9fa0283","type":"paragraph","text":"以上仰即教育所属严格遵行。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a0eeb23427","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"639e7e4c0f","type":"paragraph","text":"来源：根据文件的翻印件打印","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a0eeb23427","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}